This is the Lair of the Ninja Snowmen, located on the slopes of [[Mt. McLargeHuge]] and is unlocked by first unlocking [[The Goatlet]] and then bringing the [[The L33t Tr4pz0r's C4b1n|L33t Tr4pz0r]] the 6 [[goat cheese]]s that he has [[Mt. McLargeHuge Quest|requested]].

It is filled with Ninja Snowmen.

If your main stat is not high enough, when you try to adventure here you will get the following message:

:You near the Lair, but suddenly realize that there's no chance of you escaping a beating if you go in there. You turn around, wondering what you were thinking coming here in the first place.

:(You must have at least 53 <stat> to adventure here.)

